{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"}],"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}],"title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)isEnergySavingEnabled"},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"video frames per second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/isEnergySavingEnabled":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/isEnergySavingEnabled","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":", if automatic energy saving should be enabled. With automatic energy saving enabled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"base scanner view controller will, after a certain time of inactivity, enter the energy save mode by lowering the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"title":"isEnergySavingEnabled","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/isenergysavingenabled","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isEnergySavingEnabled"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbot